CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 28, 1953, pg, 26, reads: "Proud Champions - Here are the four Negro youths who captured the Golden Gloves titles at the Gardens Tuesday night... Andy Strong, top man in 160-pound bracket...- Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Golden Gloves boxing champion Andy Strong wearing towel around neck, posed in Duquesne Gardens with another man wearing light colored suit in background
